{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1192,"text":"Good morning, everyone."},{"time":4158,"text":"When I was first asked to do a TED Talk,"},{"time":7530,"text":"I Googled to try and find out\na little bit more about,"},{"time":12235,"text":"you know, how it felt to be giving one."},{"time":14634,"text":"And one of the first things I read\nwas a speaker in the States"},{"time":17672,"text":"saying that she felt fine\nuntil she came onstage,"},{"time":20744,"text":"and then she saw the timer ticking down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22812,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23874,"text":"And it reminded her of a bomb."},{"time":26156,"text":"I was thinking,\n\"That's the last thing I need.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":28626,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30638,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":35999,"text":"Anyway, it's a great privilege to be here."},{"time":38056,"text":"I think it's a bit of a joke"},{"time":39823,"text":"for an editor of a paper to choose\na photographer to open a speaking event."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43922,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44978,"text":"We're not renowned for our words,"},{"time":46875,"text":"and I spent the last 40 years\nhiding behind a camera"},{"time":49476,"text":"so I didn't have to speak."},{"time":51321,"text":"But I'm here today, and what I want\nto talk about are stories"},{"time":54327,"text":"and the importance of stories to me"},{"time":56128,"text":"and, I think, the importance\nof stories to everybody."},{"time":58712,"text":"I'm sure today you'll hear\na lot of stories"},{"time":61032,"text":"and, by listening to other\npeople's stories,"},{"time":63160,"text":"I think we can learn\nabout the world, about other people"},{"time":66890,"text":"and get a better understanding."},{"time":68451,"text":"So I want to talk about three stories\nthat I've done as a photographer,"},{"time":72121,"text":"and how they've inspired me,"},{"time":74119,"text":"and how, in my life, I've become\na part of the stories"},{"time":77161,"text":"that I document myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79966,"text":"As John said, I was a fashion photographer"},{"time":82169,"text":"and music photographer for 10 years."},{"time":83955,"text":"I enjoyed it, I had a lot of fun,"},{"time":85582,"text":"but always wanted to do\nsomething more with my work."},{"time":88378,"text":"And storytelling was always\nsomething I wanted to do."},{"time":92187,"text":"So 10 years ago, I set out\nto travel the world,"},{"time":95681,"text":"to go and photograph\nother people in their situations"},{"time":99840,"text":"and to record their stories,\nto bring them back,"},{"time":102598,"text":"so that other people might understand."},{"time":105072,"text":"But this didn't happen overnight."},{"time":107550,"text":"When I worked as a music photographer\nand a fashion photographer,"},{"time":110698,"text":"I always had this nagging feeling\nthat there was something missing,"},{"time":113940,"text":"that I wasn't quite\nusing my skills productively."},{"time":116974,"text":"And it may seem\nvery obvious, the link, now,"},{"time":119166,"text":"but at the time,\nI couldn't really work out"},{"time":121305,"text":"how could I use my photography\nto do something useful."},{"time":124883,"text":"So I gave up photography."},{"time":126622,"text":"I walked away from it completely\nand decided to do care work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130009,"text":"As a care worker, I started looking\nafter a young guy called Nick."},{"time":136167,"text":"Nick has autism, very severe autism."},{"time":139860,"text":"But over the years of looking after him,\nwe became very close friends."},{"time":143312,"text":"I would give him a 24-hour care,"},{"time":144975,"text":"we would go off and do things\nfrom swimming, going for walks ..."},{"time":148524,"text":"all sorts."},{"time":150526,"text":"Bit by bit, though,\nas I got to know him better,"},{"time":152824,"text":"I realized that his story\nwasn't being told."},{"time":155555,"text":"He self-harmed, he would punch himself\nquite a lot in the face."},{"time":160142,"text":"And nobody really got to see that."},{"time":165217,"text":"So this is Nick."},{"time":167576,"text":"He used to describe his life\nas living downstairs at a party."},{"time":171884,"text":"He said he could hear\nthe party in the kitchen,"},{"time":174133,"text":"but he felt like he was always\ntrapped in the basement,"},{"time":176866,"text":"in his own little world,"},{"time":178054,"text":"wanting to be part of the party\nbut not able to walk upstairs."},{"time":183010,"text":"So I documented his life."},{"time":184435,"text":"I started to photograph it,"},{"time":186398,"text":"not really with any intention\nof doing anything with the pictures,"},{"time":189518,"text":"but just as a way of recording."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191429,"text":"And as I started doing that, I realized\nthat I could tell somebody's story"},{"time":195612,"text":"through my photographs."},{"time":199161,"text":"As I said, Nick would self-harm."},{"time":201526,"text":"He would punch himself in the face."},{"time":204671,"text":"And nobody really got to see that."},{"time":209055,"text":"As we built up a kind\nof closer friendship,"},{"time":211636,"text":"he finally would allow me\nto actually see him doing this"},{"time":215862,"text":"and to document it."},{"time":217038,"text":"It was a moment of trust."},{"time":221167,"text":"The social services were not\nparticularly good at helping Nick,"},{"time":224359,"text":"and they said that he wouldn't be\nself-harming as bad as we said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228672,"text":"So one day, I took a photograph\nof when he'd really been self-harming."},{"time":234188,"text":"We took that to the social services,"},{"time":236071,"text":"and their reaction was immediately\nincredibly different,"},{"time":238854,"text":"and they managed to get a lot of help."},{"time":241221,"text":"And I'm glad to say now,\neight years later,"},{"time":243940,"text":"I actually spoke to Nick last night,"},{"time":245772,"text":"and he wanted to let me know\nthat he was feeling a lot better,"},{"time":248924,"text":"and he doesn't do\nthe self-harming anymore."},{"time":251315,"text":"And in some small way,\nI hope that the photographs"},{"time":254399,"text":"was a part of that process."},{"time":256886,"text":"The main thing it did is it inspired\nme to go out with my camera"},{"time":260716,"text":"and to tell other people's stories."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264223,"text":"One of the stories I did\nwas in Kutupalong,"},{"time":268152,"text":"on the border of Burma and Bangladesh."},{"time":272080,"text":"Here, the Rohingyas refugees\nhave been left,"},{"time":275392,"text":"pretty much to rot,"},{"time":276590,"text":"for over 20 years."},{"time":278562,"text":"This is a picture of the unofficial camp."},{"time":280807,"text":"At the top, you can see\nthe official UN camp."},{"time":284956,"text":"All these huts are the unofficial camps."},{"time":287322,"text":"Literally, the raw sewage\nruns through the camp."},{"time":291411,"text":"The people there have been forgotten,"},{"time":293703,"text":"so I thought it was important to go\nand document their stories."},{"time":296750,"text":"So I arranged with the village elder;"},{"time":298579,"text":"the people would come along the next day,"},{"time":300812,"text":"and I would take portraits\nof all these people"},{"time":303104,"text":"and record their stories."},{"time":305288,"text":"So as the time went on,\nI turned up in the morning,"},{"time":308685,"text":"I put a big, white sheet up,\nand I started to photograph these people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313792,"text":"Suddenly, though, everything\ngot a bit out of control,"},{"time":316839,"text":"and, although it was still dawn,"},{"time":318484,"text":"we were filled in this small\nlittle compound we had made"},{"time":321547,"text":"with literally hundreds of people\nturning up with ailments and diseases"},{"time":326629,"text":"and just ... a hopeless situation."},{"time":330048,"text":"And that's exactly\nwhat their situation is -- helpless."},{"time":333498,"text":"A child with a tumor that nobody helped,\nwho was slowly suffocating."},{"time":339562,"text":"I got in a bit of a panic,"},{"time":341233,"text":"because these people were\ncoming up to me, desperate,"},{"time":343752,"text":"and I was trying to explain\nto the village elder"},{"time":346033,"text":"that I was not a doctor,\nand I couldn't help these people."},{"time":348998,"text":"And the village elder\nturned to me and he said,"},{"time":351254,"text":"\"No, it's really important;\nthese people know you're not a doctor,"},{"time":354543,"text":"but at least somebody\nis now telling their story,"},{"time":356954,"text":"and somebody is recording\nwhat is happening to them.\""},{"time":360405,"text":"And it was a good moment for me."},{"time":362152,"text":"It was a realization\nthat maybe it was worthwhile"},{"time":366028,"text":"going off and doing these things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369526,"text":"Another story that inspired me\nwas in Odessa, in Ukraine."},{"time":373458,"text":"I was documenting a bunch of street kids."},{"time":376592,"text":"I ended up actually living\nwith them in a squat,"},{"time":378921,"text":"which I can say was an experience."},{"time":382262,"text":"Many late nights of vodka-fueled violence"},{"time":385191,"text":"with me sitting in the corner with my bag,"},{"time":387612,"text":"just going, \"When was this a good idea?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":389994,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391492,"text":"I would say it's moments\nlike that when I think,"},{"time":393791,"text":"\"Why did I leave the fashion world?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":395617,"text":"But they were great kids,"},{"time":396846,"text":"and on the last day,\nthey took me down to the sea"},{"time":400467,"text":"for a sort of trip, a sort of farewell."},{"time":403113,"text":"There they are, drinking vodka."},{"time":404706,"text":"And then Serge, who was the oldest\nand the most violent --"},{"time":408034,"text":"he'd just got out of the prison\nfor stabbing somebody --"},{"time":410721,"text":"comes and puts his arm around me\nand says, \"We go swimming.\""},{"time":413652,"text":"Now, I have to say, I had\na \"Lonely Planet\" guide to Ukraine"},{"time":417326,"text":"and in it, it gave some advice."},{"time":420346,"text":"And in that advice was,\n\"Do not talk to the street kids,"},{"time":425038,"text":"at no point leave your baggage unattended"},{"time":428889,"text":"and in all counts, do not go swimming.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":431354,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":433149,"text":"So I was like, \"I don't know\nif this is a good idea.\""},{"time":436904,"text":"Serge has got his arm around me."},{"time":439284,"text":"I'm like, \"OK.\" So there I am."}]},{"cues":[{"time":441035,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442069,"text":"I literally handed all my cameras,\nall my equipment, to these street kids."},{"time":445665,"text":"And they took it."},{"time":447498,"text":"It's kind of funny to know,\nif you look in the background,"},{"time":450265,"text":"you can see the other street kids\nwho didn't get in the water go,"},{"time":453362,"text":"\"Why would you get in that water?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":455033,"text":"But one of the little kids, Lilic,"},{"time":456718,"text":"he was the one who had taken my camera,"},{"time":458670,"text":"and he started taking photographs."},{"time":460339,"text":"He was really excited by this camera."},{"time":462344,"text":"And we talked a lot about\nhow I was going to get him a camera"},{"time":465277,"text":"and would return and we could start\nto teach him photography."},{"time":468275,"text":"He had a real eye for things."},{"time":470771,"text":"That's him, there."},{"time":472338,"text":"That was taken on the last\nevening I was there."},{"time":475278,"text":"I'd been staying there, but that night,\nI left to go and collect my things."},{"time":478897,"text":"And when I came back\nin the morning, he was dead."},{"time":482057,"text":"He had taken a lot of pills\nand a lot of vodka."},{"time":485103,"text":"And he had passed out in the night\nand didn’t recover."},{"time":489814,"text":"Again, it was another reminder"},{"time":491465,"text":"of maybe why I should record\nthese people's stories:"},{"time":493957,"text":"because their lives are important,"},{"time":495614,"text":"and it's important\nfor me to document them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498147,"text":"Then in February of last year,\nwhen I was on patrol in Afghanistan,"},{"time":502848,"text":"I stepped on an IED."},{"time":506002,"text":"That's me down there, somewhere."},{"time":509178,"text":"I became part of the story."},{"time":511617,"text":"At first, I was devastated\nby what had happened, obviously."},{"time":516598,"text":"I thought my work was over,"},{"time":518520,"text":"I thought -- everything\ndidn't make sense to me."},{"time":522423,"text":"And then I realized:\nI never set out to Congo,"},{"time":525470,"text":"to Angola, to Bangladesh"},{"time":527282,"text":"to take photographs."},{"time":528906,"text":"I went to those places because I wanted\nto make some kind of change,"},{"time":532406,"text":"and photography happened to be my tool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535402,"text":"And then I became aware\nthat my body was, in many ways,"},{"time":539219,"text":"a living example\nof what war does to somebody."},{"time":541752,"text":"And I realized I could use\nmy own experience, my own body,"},{"time":545359,"text":"to tell that story."},{"time":547165,"text":"And it was also by looking back\nat the other people I've documented."},{"time":551072,"text":"I thought of Nick, and I thought\nof his resilience."},{"time":554429,"text":"I thought of the Rohingyas\nand the fact that they have no hope."},{"time":559023,"text":"I thought of Lilic and a lost life."},{"time":562880,"text":"And in fact, it was the stories\nthat I've documented"},{"time":565359,"text":"that inspired me to get\nthrough the last year,"},{"time":568592,"text":"to survive,"},{"time":570408,"text":"to get back up on my new legs"},{"time":572481,"text":"and to be able to come\nand tell their stories,"},{"time":574918,"text":"but also my own story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577346,"text":"So I did a self-portrait,"},{"time":580046,"text":"because I wanted to show everybody\nwhat a bomb does to somebody,"},{"time":583250,"text":"but also to show that losing your limbs\ndoesn't end your life;"},{"time":587390,"text":"that you can have\nwhat people say is disability,"},{"time":589812,"text":"but not be disabled;"},{"time":591302,"text":"that you can be able to do anything"},{"time":593119,"text":"if you put your mind to it"},{"time":594984,"text":"and have belief in it."},{"time":598389,"text":"It's strange,"},{"time":599570,"text":"but in many ways I look\nat where I was a year ago,"},{"time":601987,"text":"and I look at where I am now,"},{"time":603449,"text":"and I realize that I have\na lot of things I didn't have then."},{"time":606378,"text":"I wouldn't be sitting here right now\nif this hadn't happened."},{"time":609315,"text":"I wouldn't have been able\nto show you those photographs"},{"time":611951,"text":"and tell you those stories."},{"time":613364,"text":"I was lucky 10 years ago,\nwhen I sat down and I tried to work out"},{"time":616846,"text":"what I could do to make\na difference in this world."},{"time":619291,"text":"I realized that my photography\nwas a tool and a way to do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623175,"text":"I think that's what's really key."},{"time":625345,"text":"It's that we all can\nbe part of that wheel."},{"time":628624,"text":"We can all be cogs in a wheel of change."},{"time":631107,"text":"We can all make a difference."},{"time":632691,"text":"Everybody here has an ability\nto use something"},{"time":635533,"text":"to make a difference to the world."},{"time":637265,"text":"We can all sit in front of the TV and go,"},{"time":640263,"text":"\"I don't know what to do\nabout it,\" and forget about it."},{"time":642955,"text":"But the reality is that we can\nall do something."},{"time":645259,"text":"It might be just writing a letter."},{"time":647069,"text":"It might be standing\non a soapbox and talking."},{"time":649603,"text":"It might be just recording\nsomebody's story"},{"time":651701,"text":"and telling it to somebody else."},{"time":653356,"text":"But every single one of us here,"},{"time":655173,"text":"if we want to make a difference, we can,\nan there is nothing to stop us."},{"time":658656,"text":"And we all have our own experiences\nthat we can use as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662548,"text":"So really, that's all I wanted\nto talk about today."},{"time":665001,"text":"I just wanted to say that life\ngoes on all around the world."},{"time":670090,"text":"People are going through terrible things."},{"time":673164,"text":"Everyone of us is going\nthrough our own terrible experience."},{"time":676048,"text":"But if we share those\nand we talk about stories,"},{"time":678386,"text":"then we can inspire each other"},{"time":679906,"text":"to get through our own bad experiences."},{"time":682592,"text":"I know that the people I've recorded\nhave gotten me to this point."},{"time":686370,"text":"And I hope in some small way,\nthe stories I've been able to tell you"},{"time":689695,"text":"will help you get through things."},{"time":691313,"text":"And in turn, I hope you will use\nyour experiences to help others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695624,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696831,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}